title: Suncoast Classic
text: The Suncoast Classic was a <a href="golf">golf</a> tournament on the <a href="Southern%20Africa">Southern Africa</a> based <a href="Sunshine%20Tour">Sunshine Tour</a>. It was founded in 2006 and has always been held at the Durban Country Club in <a href="Durban">Durban</a>, <a href="KwaZulu-Natal">KwaZulu-Natal</a>, <a href="South%20Africa">South Africa</a>.
